albums.title: The Mission
albums.subtitle: Central California
albums.description: Along the old road stretching from San Francisco to the tip of Baja lies a string of missions. Unknown to most travelers passing by on the freeway, they still stand guard over the brush. Our history.

albums.title: O'Farrel and Polk
albums.subtitle: Flotsam and Jetsam
albums.description: I'm on Polk street, between O'Farrel and Ellis. Scenes of a shuttered San Francisco. Broken people on the street. fentanyl. The flotsam and jetsam of a strange twisted time. He runs up to me. “He, hey, you better get out of here with that camera. My buddy back there’s got a slingshot. he’s gonna bust your head right open if you don’t get out of here”. A rock hits my leg as I leave.
